Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不来？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这不是很好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:01 WEIRD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非这样做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一定要想清楚……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……即使不在这世界也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我无关 我什么也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也离不开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能静一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快一点 走快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉 不要在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 只是一场恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的 茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没收到那东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-MAIL？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由四方田千砂寄来的E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太会用电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总还得天天查查E-MAIL吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为玲音还是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会哭成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她收到了千砂的E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂的……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D班的同学 上星期在涉谷跳楼自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也提过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只茱莉收到过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已有好几位同学在这个星期也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，她已经……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 死人是不会送E-MAIL的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们真的收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在她死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛…(笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOG IN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 请念出姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音频核对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定 你是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在查阅资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已接收给玲音的电子邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四方田千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要读取E-MAIL吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾在放学后一同回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我只是抛弃了我的肉体

Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在另一个空间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才发E-MAIL给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在不明白也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟早会明白的 大家也都会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要死？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人写恶作剧E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成谣言散布在学校中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你知道那并不是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要死？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里  有神的存在

Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很晚才吃午餐 我饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了一封E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上个星期自杀的那位同学寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很少来这房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那一部……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那部电脑是新型的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于对它有兴趣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音已经是个中学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定比朋友们晚了一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要用更新的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 这个世界是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在真实的世界或是网上的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类都需要交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样世界才会进步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像玲音这样的小孩子 一定很快就能交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妈妈总是不明白这道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是怕怎样 只是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么突然说这些呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想见面的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车因事故需要暂停行驶 不便之处 敬请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 有意外吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩仓同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩仓同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一题考试会考喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上网来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
